===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Oracle bone script: {{Han compound|宀|工|廾|ls=ic|t1=house|t2=two items|t3=two hands}} – stuffing the house with items. Hence, the original version is [[𡨄]], a character similar but unrelated to [[共]] but partly related to [[展]].

''{{w|Shuowen}}'': {{Han compound|𡨄|土|ls=ic|t2=soil}}; the bottom component was added later.

